I have been so so blessed in my career and it just keeps coming! I’m moving salons at the end of the month!! I have been given the greatest opportunity to work alongside @skinmcl in a suite at their medical office! 💅🏽 
I’m so excited for this growth opportunity, as sad as it is to leave @mysa.suites!! They’ve been great to me over here!! 🥲 

I understand if some of you won’t be able to travel further for your appointment, but I’d love it if you could! I will message all of my clients once I’m all moved and ready to go! The address is 2150 N main st, North Logan. It’s about 10 minutes north of the salon I currently work at, so plan accordingly!! Can’t wait to see you all there🥹🩷 Please message me with any questions or concerns! (ALSO!! keep your eyes peeled, I have more CRAZY news coming up!!!) ✨
